page_0: "Garrett,

As you might have guessed already, the body you found near the last glyph was mine. I had died already before you arrived, and all that is left of me is this mind construct the Sanctuary glyph created. As long as I cannot find any rest, this sphere of reality and the glyphs connected to it will continue to exist and allow me to communicate with you. 

The war hammer Draeworek is very close. You have to find a way to destroy it, but remember that you must not touch it. Any direct contact would immediately kill you."
page_1: "I am sorry I could not be of more help. Honestly, I am surprised I even made it this far. After all, I'm a librarian, not an adventurer.

Farewell,
Keeper Aleph"
